reviews.review_text:
bad matrix this is the second 'matrix' by 'photoleon' that sounded 'flanged'
 seemed out of phase, Seamons, Dusborne, Chappell,
never fail this hurtle....Seamons often improves the sound/show

maybe photoleon needs a call from audioleon
